metadata.name: NoNameCharli #1
metadata.description:
NoNameCharli is a 5000 meme NFT collection celebrating ALL THINGS BLOCKCHAIN.

It's not only memes designed to go viral and spread awareness, but also an iconic art collection to be seen as a timestamp of this revolutionary technology called blockchain in 2022, amidst the backdrop of a historic time we are all living through. 

Memes, Art Collection, Social Commentary, Utility, Education, Virality, Branding. 
There has never been a collection like this. It's NEW!

Imagine a collection like this of the "internet" in 1988...
